@page "/office"
@attribute [Authorize]

<PageTitle>Team Office - AI Team Dashboard</PageTitle>

<div class="coming-soon-container">
    <div class="coming-soon-card">
        <h2>Team Office</h2>
        <p>3D 等角視角辦公室視覺化介面</p>
        <p class="coming-soon-label">規劃中，敬請期待</p>
        <ul class="coming-soon-features">
            <li>每個 Agent 有獨立座位</li>
            <li>點擊 Agent 展開詳細資訊面板</li>
            <li>Agent 依狀態有對應動畫（忙碌打字、閒置發呆、錯誤冒汗）</li>
            <li>休息區（閒置時移動）</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
